             was indicted for <rs id="t17980912-26-off142" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980912-26-off142" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980912-26-off142" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17980912-26-cd143" type="crimeDate">26th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-26-off142 t17980912-26-cd143"></join>, three linen shifts, value 21s. a pair of sheets, value 21s. a towel, value 6d. four pair of silk stockings, value 40s. four other silk stockings; value 2s. and two linen aprons, value 6d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980912-26-victim297" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Chaloner
                        <interp inst="t17980912-26-victim297" type="surname" value="Chaloner"></interp>
